# Currency Converter

This is a simple currency converter web application that allows users to convert between different currencies using real-time exchange rates.

## Features

- Convert between various currencies with real-time exchange rates.
- Select currencies using dropdown menus.
- Easily swap the selected currencies by clicking on an exchange rate icon.
- Automatically updates the converted amount when the input amount or selected currencies change.

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Usage

1. Open the `index.html` file in your web browser.
2. Enter the amount you want to convert in the input field.
3. Select the currency you want to convert from and the currency you want to convert to using the dropdown menus.
4. Click the "Convert" button to see the converted amount.
5. To swap the selected currencies, simply click on the exchange rate icon located between the currency selection dropdowns.

## Credits

- Currency exchange rates data provided by [Fawaz Ahmed's Currency API](https://github.com/fawazahmed0/currency-api).
